N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 80.122 - Enforcement

State Regulations

It shall be the duty of the department to enforce all of the provisions of article 33 of the Public Health Law and all of the rules, regulations and determinations made thereunder. Notes
